author: Adam K. Raymond
title: Members of Congress Who Have Tested Positive for Coronavirus
description: Three members of Congress have tested positive COVID-19, so far.
content: Members of Congress travel a lot. They meet a lot of people, shake a lot of hands and kiss a lot of babies. It was only a matter of time before those in the House and Senate began testing positive for the coronavirus. So far, three members, two in the House a… [+2878 chars]
